What AuthMiddleware Logic Should Contain Step-by-step:
1.Extract Authorization header
2.Validate format: Bearer <token> 
3.Parse JWT
4.Verify signature
5.Verify algorithm (important security check)
6.Verify expiry (exp)
7.Optionally verify issuer (iss)
8.Optionally verify audience (aud)
9.Extract claims (user_id, email)
10.Build SecurityContext
11.Attach to request context
12.Call next handler
If ANY step fails → return 401.

